                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/oed/press-center/Press-releases/2010/broad-interest-for-mature-areas-on-the-n.html?id=614360" title="">
                        Broad interest for mature areas on the Norwegian shelf
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none">Awards in Predefined Areas (APA) 2010</h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[16.09.2010]</p>
                <p>By the deadline for applications in the Awards in Predefined Areas (APA) 2010 on the Norwegian continental shelf (NCS), the Ministry of Petroleum and Energy has received applications from 41 companies. The Ministry aims at award of new production licenses in APA 2010 late 2010 or early 2011.</p>
                
                
