                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/oed/press-center/Press-releases/2010/More-knowledge-before-new-awards.html?id=607529" title="">
                        More knowledge before new awards
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[08.06.2010]</p>
                <p>The Minister of Petroleum and Energy, Mr. Terje Riis-Johansen, spoke today on a conference concerning the Integrated Management plan of the Marine Environment of the Barents Sea and the Sea Areas off the Lofoten Islands.  In light of the Deepwater Horizon accident in the Gulf of Mexico, the minister emphasized the need for more knowledge about the accident before awarding new areas for deep water exploration in the 21. licensing round.</p>
                
                
